Creating a Dockerfile:

$ mkdir Dockerfiles
$ cd Dockerfiles/
$ touch Dockerfiles
$ vim dockerfile 


Now press I for inserting in your dockerfile


FROM ubuntu
RUN apt-get update 
CMD ["echo" , " Hello world from my first docker image "]


Press Esc to switch into Command mode 
Press !wq to save and exit from the file 

$ docker build -t <image_name along with : tag>            { Image will be created here }
$ docker images
$ docker run <image_id>                                    { Conatiner will be made here }
